<sc id="1_Tesalonicenses-5">
<cm>
<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-1">
But concerning the times and the seasons, brothers, you
 have no need that anything be written to you.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Pero</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4012,1,">respecto a</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,3,"><wi type="G" value="5550,4,">los tiempos</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,5,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,6,"><wi type="G" value="2540,7,">las estaciones</wi></wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3756,9,">no</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2192,11,">tienen</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="80,8,">hermanos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="5532,10,">necesidad</wi> de que
<wi type="G" value="5213,12,">les</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1125,13,">escriba</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-2">
For you yourselves know
well that the day of the Lord comes like a thief in the night.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1063,2,">Pues</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,1,">ustedes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1492,4,">saben</wi>
<wi type="G" value="199,3,">bien</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3754,5,">que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,6,"><wi type="G" value="2250,7,">el día</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2962,8,">del Señor</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2064,14,">viene</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3779,13,">así</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5613,9,">como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2812,10,">ladrón</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,11,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3571,12,">la noche</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-3">
For when
they are saying, «Peace and safety,» then sudden destruction will come on
them, like birth pains on a pregnant woman; and they will in no way escape.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1063,2,">Pues</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3752,1,">cuando</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3004,3,">digan</wi>
«<wi type="G" value="1515,4,">Paz</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,5,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="803,6,">seguridad</wi>,»
<wi type="G" value="5119,7,">entonces</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,9,">les</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2186,10,">vendrá</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3639,11,">destrucción</wi>
<wi type="G" value="160,8,">repentina</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="5618,12,">como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,13,"><wi type="G" value="5604,14,">dolores de
parto</wi></wi> de una
<wi type="G" value="3588,15,"/><wi type="G" value="1722,16,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1064,17,">embarazo</wi>;
<wi type="G" value="2532,19,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3756,20,"><wi type="G" value="3361,21,">no</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2192,18,">tendrán</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1628,22,">escapatoria</wi>.
</t>

</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-4">
But you, brothers, aren´t in darkness, that the day should overtake
you like a thief.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Pero</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5210,1,">ustedes</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="80,3,">hermanos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3756,4,">no</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2075,5,">están</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,6,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4655,7,">oscuridad</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2443,8,">para que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,9,">aquel</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2250,10,">día</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,11,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2638,14,">sorprenda</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5613,12,">como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2812,13,">un ladrón</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-5">
You are all children of light, and children of
the day. We don´t belong to the night, nor to darkness,
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3956,1,">Todos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5210,2,">ustedes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2075,5,">son</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5207,3,">hijos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5457,4,">de la luz</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,6,">e</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5207,7,">hijos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2250,8,">del día</wi>.
<wi type="G" value="3756,9,">No</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2070,10,">somos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3571,11,">de la noche</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3761,12,">ni</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4655,13,">de la oscuridad</wi>,
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-6">
so then let´s not sleep, as the rest do, but let´s watch and be sober.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="686,1,"/><wi type="G" value="3767,2,">entonces</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3361,3,">no</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2518,4,">durmamos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,6,"/><wi type="G" value="5613,5,">como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,7,"/><wi type="G" value="3062,8,">los demás</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="235,9,">sino</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1127,10,">vigilemos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,11,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3525,12,">estemos sobrios</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-7">
For those who
sleep, sleep in the night, and those who are drunken are drunken in the
night.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1063,2,">Pues</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,1,">los que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2518,3,">duermen</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3571,4,">en la noche</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2518,5,">duermen</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,6,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,7,">los que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3182,8,">se embriagan</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3571,9,">en la noche</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3184,10,">se embriagan</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-8">
But let us, since we belong to the day, be sober, putting on the
breastplate of faith and love, and, for a helmet, the hope of salvation.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Pero</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2249,1,">nosotros</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5607,4,">que somos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2250,3,">del día</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3525,5,">estemos sobrios</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="1746,6,">poniéndonos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2382,7,">la coraza</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4102,8,">de la fe</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,9,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="26,10,">el amor</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,11,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4030,12,">por casco</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="1680,13,">la esperanza</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4991,14,">de la salvación</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-9">
For God didn´t appoint us to wrath, but to the obtaining of salvation
through our Lord Jesus Christ,
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3754,1,">Pues</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,5,"><wi type="G" value="2316,6,">Dios</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="3756,2,">no</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2248,4,">nos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5087,3,">ha determinado</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1519,7,">para</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3709,8,">ira</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="235,9,">sino</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1519,10,">para</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4047,11,">alcanzar</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4991,12,">salvación</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1223,13,">mediante</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2257,16,">nuestro</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,14,"><wi type="G" value="2962,15,">Señor</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2424,17,">Jesús</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5547,18,">Cristo</wi>,
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-10">
who died for us, that, whether we wake
or sleep, we should live together with him.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3588,1,">quien</wi>
<wi type="G" value="599,2,">murió</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5228,3,">por</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2257,4,">nosotros</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2443,5,">para que</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="1535,6,">si</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1127,7,">estemos despiertos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1535,8,">o</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2518,9,">durmamos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2198,13,">vivamos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="260,10,">juntamente</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4862,11,">con</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,12,">Él</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-11">
Therefore exhort one
another, and build each other up, even as you
<wi type="T" value="P"/> also do.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1352,1,">Entonces</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3870,2,">anímense</wi>
<wi type="G" value="240,3,">entre ustedes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,4,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3618,5,">edifíquense</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,7,"/><wi type="G" value="1520,8,">unos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1520,6,">a otros</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2531,9,">así como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,10,">también</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4160,11,">lo han hecho</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-12">
But we beg
you, brothers, to know those who labor among you, and are over you in the
Lord, and admonish you,
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,3,">les</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2065,1,">rogamos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="80,4,">hermanos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="1492,5,">que reconozcan</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,6,"/><wi type="G" value="2872,7,">a los que laboran</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,8,">entre</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5213,9,">ustedes</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,10,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4291,11,">que están sobre</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5216,12,">ustedes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,13,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2962,14,">el Señor</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,15,">y</wi>
que <wi type="G" value="5209,17,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3560,16,">amonestan</wi>,
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-13">
and to respect and honor them in love for their
work´s sake.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="2532,1,">y</wi>
que <wi type="G" value="846,3,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2233,2,">tengan</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5228,4,">en muy</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4057,5,">alta</wi>
<wi type="GC" value="2">estima</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,6,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="26,7,">amor</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1223,8,">por causa</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,11,">de su</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,9,"><wi type="G" value="2041,10,">trabajo</wi></wi>.</t>
<cl/>
Be at peace among yourselves.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1514,12,">Estén en paz</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,13,">entre</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1438,14,">ustedes</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-14">
We exhort you, brothers, admonish the
disorderly, encourage the fainthearted, support the weak, be patient toward
all.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,3,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3870,1,">exhortamos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="80,4,">hermanos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3560,5,">amonesten</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,6,">a los que</wi>  están
<wi type="G" value="813,7,">en desorden</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3888,8,">conforten a</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,9,"/><wi type="G" value="3642,10,">los quebrantados</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="472,11,">soporten a</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,12,"/><wi type="G" value="772,13,">los débiles</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3114,14,">sean pacientes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4314,15,">con</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,16,">todos</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-15">
See that no one returns evil for evil to anyone, but always follow
after that which is good, for one another, and for all.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3708,1,">Miren que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3361,2,"><wi type="G" value="5100,3,">ninguno</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="591,8,">devuelva</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2556,4,">mal</wi>
<wi type="G" value="473,5,">por</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2556,6,">mal</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5100,7,">a nadie</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="235,9,">pero</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3842,10,">siempre</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1377,13,">sigan</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,11,"/><wi type="G" value="18,12,">lo bueno</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,14,">tanto</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1519,15,">entre</wi>
<wi type="G" value="240,16,">ustedes</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,17,">como</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1519,18,">para</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,19,">todos</wi>.</t>
</sv></cm>

<cm>
<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-16">
Rejoice always.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="5463,2,">Alégrense</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3842,1,">siempre</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-17">
Pray without ceasing.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="4336,2,">Oren</wi>
<wi type="G" value="89,1,">sin cesar</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-18">
In everything give
thanks, for this is the will of God in Christ Jesus toward you.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1722,1,">En</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,2,">todo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2168,3,">den gracias</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="1063,5,">pues</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5124,4,">esta</wi> es
<wi type="G" value="2307,6,">la voluntad</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2316,7,">de Dios</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,8,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5547,9,">Cristo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2424,10,">Jesús</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1519,11,">para</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,12,">ustedes</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-19">
Don´t quench the Spirit.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3361,3,">No</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4570,4,">apaguen</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,1,"><wi type="G" value="4151,2,">al Espíritu</wi></wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-20">
Don´t despise prophesies.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3361,2,">No</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1848,3,">desprecien</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4394,1,">las profecías</wi>. </t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-21">
Test all things, and hold firmly that which is good.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1381,2,">Prueben</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,1,">todo</wi>, y
<wi type="G" value="2722,5,">mantengan</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,3,">lo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2570,4,">bueno</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-22">
Abstain from every form of evil.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="567,5,">Absténganse</wi>
<wi type="G" value="575,1,">de</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,2,">toda</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1491,3,">forma</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4190,4,">de maldad</wi>.</t>
</sv></cm><cm>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-23">
May the God of peace himself sanctify you completely. May your whole
spirit, soul, and body be preserved blameless at the coming of our Lord Jesus
Christ.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,2,">Y</wi>
que
<wi type="G" value="846,1,">el mismo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,3,"><wi type="G" value="2316,4,">Dios</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,5,"><wi type="G" value="1515,6,">de paz</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,8,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="37,7,">santifique</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3651,9,">completamente</wi>.
<wi type="G" value="2532,10,">Y</wi> que
<wi type="G" value="3648,11,">todo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5216,12,">su</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,13,"><wi type="G" value="4151,14,">espíritu</wi></wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,15,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,16,"><wi type="G" value="5590,17,">alma</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,18,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,19,"><wi type="G" value="4983,20,">cuerpo</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="5083,30,">sea preservado</wi>
<wi type="G" value="274,21,">irreprensible</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,22,">hasta</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,23,"><wi type="G" value="3952,24,">el advenimiento</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2257,27,">de nuestro</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,25,"><wi type="G" value="2962,26,">Señor</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="2424,28,">Jesús</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5547,29,">Cristo</wi>.
</t>

</sv></cm><cm>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-24">
Faithful is he who calls you, who will also do it.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="4103,1,">Fiel</wi> es
<wi type="G" value="3588,2,">el que</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5209,4,">los</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2564,3,">llamó</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="3739,5,">quien</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,6,">también</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4160,7,">hará</wi>.
</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-25">
Brothers, pray for us.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="80,1,">Hermanos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="4336,2,">oren</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4012,3,">por</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2257,4,">nosotros</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-26">
Greet all the brothers with a holy kiss.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="782,1,">Saluden a</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,4,">todos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,2,"><wi type="G" value="80,3,">los hermanos</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="1722,5,">con</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5370,6,">un beso</wi>
<wi type="G" value="40,7,">santo</wi>.</t>
</sv>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-27">
I solemnly
charge you by the Lord that this letter be read to all the holy brothers.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="5209,2,">Les</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3726,1,">encomiendo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,3,"><wi type="G" value="2962,4,">en el Señor</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="314,5,">que lean</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,6,">esta</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1992,7,">carta</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,8,">a todos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,9,"/><wi type="G" value="40,10,">los santos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="80,11,">hermanos</wi>.
</t>
</sv></cm><cm>

<sv id="1_Tesalonicenses-5-28">
The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you. Amen.
